        </div>
        <div class="grid-main__content grid-main__content--narrow">
            <p class="dropcap">We communicated the way the new system worked to our marketing team and trained them on how to use it. It was a really big success. Work that used to take days or weeks and required just about all of one of our team member’s time now only took a few hours. We put the power entirely in the hands of our marketing team by building tools to help them create specialized work without needing to involve the developer team at all. Empowering others to do their best work with something that I build is very satisfying for me.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
